Welcome to Sugar Beach Golf & Spa Resort, Mauritius Your plantation-style resort
The Sugar Beach Resort & Spa unfurls along an exceptional stretch of beach and lagoon on the sun-drenched west coast.
Steeped in time-honoured traditions, lifestyle here is infused with tasteful elegance whilst ensuring ultimate current-day comforts and conveniences.
Gastronomy is open to the world's cuisines, celebrating fresh seafood and local delicacies.
Come sunset, social scenes radiate with warmth and pick up effervescence into the night. Read more
The famous hotel situated on the west coast is celebrating its 20th anniversary this year and is connecting with Tamarina Golf Club to offer a new golfing experience to all its guests.
The Tamarina Golf Club has an 18-hole championship course designed by the American golf architect, Rodney Wright.
The golf course proposes five starting options for each hole: (...)
Timeless Memories at Sun Resorts A wealth of possibilities for fulfilling moments and emotions
Live Video Get a glimpse of the beauty of Sugar Beach from the live video.
Mauritius flavours at the resort Mauritian gastronomy holds no secrets for the bold chefs at the restaurants of the chic Sugar Beach.
Inspired by the idyllic surroundings of the hotel, they never tire of reinterpreting typically Mauritian recipes and changing perceptions.
If each dish is a delight for the taste buds, then the presentation is also a feast for the eyes.
The cuisine on offer at the Tides restaurant is delicious and far exceeds the expectations of even the most demanding gourmets.
With an atmosphere that is both contemporary and casual, this is a delightfully original kitchen, with its feet firmly in the white sand.
Truly a stunning setting for your Mauritius holiday, in gastronomic heaven. Read more
Your hotel on video Watch our videos to discover our hotel.
A taste of what lies ahead on your stay in Mauritius !
